NOTE ON THE FACE-EMBEDDING MODEL: this MIT license covers the source code only;
bundled model weights carry their own licenses. The packaged `.app`/`.dmg` bundles
AuraFace v1 (Apache-2.0, https://huggingface.co/fal/AuraFace-v1) — commercial-clean
and free to redistribute. A plain `swift build` uses Apple Vision (no model, no
restriction). ArcFace `buffalo_l` (InsightFace) is an optional higher-accuracy swap
but is NON-COMMERCIAL (personal use only) and is NOT distributed with this repository;
do not attach a buffalo_l-bundled `.app`/`.dmg` to a public release. EdgeFace is also
non-commercial (CC BY-NC-SA). See docs/MODELS.md before redistributing any build.
